{"tid":1178002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中文宣] 香港人，你準備好享受來自支 #陽光司法 嘅尊享禮遇未呀？","createTime":"2019-05-30T06:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T06:56:35.000Z","uid":254183,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b6bcd0f686a106a1bce4f22048f85b2dd42b75a3","tid":1178002,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS2gWpR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS2gWpR.png&h=7bbf5dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為咗俾大家有萬全嘅思想準備，我哋特登整咗張「送中後懶人包」，俾大家share俾一家大細親戚朋友齊齊學習！<br />\n<br />\n驚八款禮遇太多揀唔落手咩？冇有怕！通過咗送中條例修訂之後，香港人就可以一齊食全餐㗎喇！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係死都啃唔落，6月9日就記得上街「D7」個 #唔死都冇用 嘅 #八婆林鄭 喇！<br />\n<br />\n【守護香港反送中】<br />\n日期：2019年6月9日<br />\n時間：2:30集合；3:00起步<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣東角道 至 立法會<br />\n<br />\n製作者: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sagohk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsagohk%2F&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1egMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=8c24aa23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sagohk/</a>"},{"pid":"23769c076e0aed98fec265f73a9cd4f7cdd30da1","tid":1178002,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be10313956bcbcc2c4264e3c5e28a1302452c06e","tid":1178002,"uid":193713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45c0794087cc1252ddf98e223b4fb3d8341849b2","tid":1178002,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e84589d73d9d3ce23bd89650aca06557a50ba2d","tid":1178002,"uid":65603,"